{"tid":258963,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"李卓人：呼籲市民「記得帶錢嚟」六四","createTime":"2017-05-26T14:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T06:56:39.000Z","uid":731,"like":4,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"889efd15ddd2e4a10bd2e6a52ab042eff249e03b","tid":258963,"uid":731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"李卓人特別呼籲市民「記得帶錢嚟」，用以支持支聯會營運六四臨時紀念館。他指，若要年輕人繼續了解六四真相，紀念館是其中一個方法，去年已有8間學校到場參觀。他希望可以盡快找到地方和資金，建立六四永久紀念館。<br />\n<br />\n另外，支聯會後日（28日）亦會舉辦遊行，下午3時從灣仔修頓球場出發，遊行至中聯辦。蔡耀昌指，28年前的百萬人遊行，同樣是5月28日星期天舉行，呼籲市民周日能參與遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qni9tq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qni9tq&d=EkSOzQ7ZVjnG5t8dBASUihOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=28b0f65a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qni9tq</a>"},{"pid":"1c3f354a9c4a7ba0d6bd29998856cc3339ef5ba9","tid":258963,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640a6511c5838fdd95f184b80ff4d101e02344e4","tid":258963,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:16:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e85a84fad51dd37b6655e18e50e453501027fcb","tid":258963,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，政治乞兒"},{"pid":"a4117690c70e273590c27be80cd70c8b81149483","tid":258963,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b6557e4227478f4359027127b69841bae5b7d2","tid":258963,"uid":4440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6dc780ca97c0f592949e8c9db2cbefc3b01c753","tid":258963,"uid":9608,"like":2,"dislike":